data.description: Soothing coastal serenity in this large home at the Key West Golf Club gated community!  Tucked inside lush tropical landscaping, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms, two full bathrooms, impact rated windows & doors, stacked impact sliding glass doors that open onto the covered back porch with glistening lake views framed by a veil of privacy from a mature Seagrape tree.  The luxury vinyl plank floors offer a low maintenance, easy care coastal lifestyle.  Soak away the day with easy access to both Golf Club pools: the tucked away pool nicknamed the 'locals pool' & the stunning resort style pool at the Clubhouse, masterfully designed with beautiful shaded nooks shaded by swaying palm fronds. Transferable flood insurance, & low wind insurance!  Explore the Zen garden, butterfly garden, & full gym, all on-site!  This impeccably maintained home is a spectacular find, one to not miss!  VA Assumable Loan at 4.5% rate available to eligible Buyers!
